00:39:48.090 --> 00:39:52.180
How much extra work is
it to add an ATAG check

00:39:52.180 --> 00:39:54.257
to your accessibility audit,

00:39:54.258 --> 00:39:57.520
and where would you
put it in the process?

00:40:01.100 --> 00:40:06.960
 <v Helen> It incorporates
WCAG, If it's just for me

00:40:06.960 --> 00:40:12.110
and my personal use,
I do part B on the items I'm using

00:40:12.110 --> 00:40:15.510
to make sure that if I'm
producing content that I'm able

00:40:15.510 --> 00:40:20.740
to not be blocked It's like when I
get enforced, the company says I have

00:40:20.740 --> 00:40:25.050
to use this product and then I
can't create graphs for my reports

00:40:25.050 --> 00:40:26.050
that are accessible.

00:40:26.960 --> 00:40:28.300
It's so frustrating.

00:40:28.300 --> 00:40:32.380
And it's that sort of thing,
making sure that I can do what I need

00:40:32.380 --> 00:40:34.260
to do without getting frustrated.

00:40:35.380 --> 00:40:36.610
So that doesn't take a lot.

00:40:36.610 --> 00:40:38.500
And that's just a common
sense kind of thing.

00:40:38.500 --> 00:40:43.500
But when it comes to the audit
itself, it doesn't take a lot extra

00:40:43.500 --> 00:40:46.590
from the WCAG because
you quite often

00:40:46.590 --> 00:40:50.100
from doing the web content
accessibility guideline checks,

00:40:50.100 --> 00:40:52.350
you will notice the
alternative text,

00:40:52.350 --> 00:40:56.370
you'll notice the keyboard
accessibility and so on,

00:40:56.370 --> 00:40:58.290
because that's part of it there.

00:40:59.380 --> 00:41:02.110
But remember if you're using
an application it's not going

00:41:02.110 --> 00:41:04.410
to be like for like with
websites where you've got

00:41:04.410 --> 00:41:07.050
the same keyboard shortcuts.

00:41:07.050 --> 00:41:14.030
So one thing I recommend when
it comes to ATAG is making sure

00:41:14.030 --> 00:41:16.040
that it is an authoring
tool first off.

00:41:16.040 --> 00:41:18.740
If it's not an authoring tool,
you're not creating content.

00:41:18.740 --> 00:41:20.310
If it's really easy,
don't do it at all.

00:41:21.450 --> 00:41:25.590
But when it comes to creating
content, it's important on a personal

00:41:25.590 --> 00:41:30.140
and on an audit way
because it does extras.

00:41:30.140 --> 00:41:33.460
It's like it's looking at the
support, it's looking at the help.

00:41:33.460 --> 00:41:35.060
And that doesn't
take too long at all.

00:41:35.060 --> 00:41:39.450
If it takes you a long time to do
that part, it's not accessible.

00:41:39.450 --> 00:41:40.640
That's always a big giveaway.

00:41:41.790 --> 00:41:42.560
So yes.

