When you're trying
to create content,

00:42:01.730 --> 00:42:03.890
if it's something that's
rendering your content,

00:42:03.890 --> 00:42:06.120
then that's user agent
accessibility guidelines.

00:42:07.450 --> 00:42:10.180
I know that when I first
started doing mobile testing,

00:42:10.181 --> 00:42:12.044
everyone's like, Oh,
WC, it doesn't count.

00:42:12.045 --> 00:42:13.430
